snippet.title: SRB2Kart v2  - Dark Fortress Showcase - 3 Year Anniversary Preview
snippet.description:
Textures: https://twitter.com/troopsushi (primary) | Chengi, VelocitOni (minor)
Mapping: Chromatian (primary) | Chengi, TehRealSalt
Results music: Leila Wilson (Sonic 3 Alternate Album) - Competition Menu

Introducing Dark Fortress Zone from the popular Romhack, "Sonic Megamix" (initially by Stealth and Team Megamix)...particularly the fan-recreation, Sonic Megamix Mania!

Avoid molten lava and dangerous dungeon traps as you Sliptide through this mountain stronghold. Utilize the new Trick Panels (Mechanic shown in video not final) to take unique shortcuts and snag powerups while gaining a burst of speed!

...And watch your tires on those stairs! Those karts aren't as stable as they used to be..

DISCORD: http://discord.gg/WJmqDtN
TWITTER: https://twitter.com/KartKrewDev
MEGAMIX MANIA: https://twitter.com/megamixmania
